						<h1>How to Sell Your Las Vegas Home Today!</h1>
<h1>*Leslie's Marketing Plan For Success!</h1>
<p>When you're ready to take the next step toward <a href="/selling.php" target="_self">selling your home in Las Vegas</a>, I am here to help. Based on my twelve years of experience, I know the Las Vegas real estate market and can give you expert advice for your individual situation. I will sit down with you for a free one-on-one consultation, and deliver a comprehensive data profile of your local area &amp; property.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Seller Testimonial:</strong> "Leslie recently sold my Summerlin home after only 9 days on the market with multiple offers. I interviewed 3 realtors and Leslie had the most comprehensive comparison and marketing plan"... <a href="/testimonials.php">See More Testimonials</a></p>
</blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img title="Home selling process for Leslie Hoke, Las Vegas realtor" src="http://www.lasvegashomesbyleslie.com/images/selling-process-900_900.jpg" alt="Home selling process for Leslie Hoke, Las Vegas realtor" width="900" height="538" /></p>
<h3>Steps for Selling Your Las Vegas Valley Home</h3>
<p>Have you ever wondered what goes in to marketing a Las Vegas home for sale? The following "how to guide" lists the steps for selling your Las Vegas Valley home or condo for maximum exposure.</p>
<h4>1. Comparable Market Analysis (CMA)</h4>
<p>Deciding whether or not it’s time to sell your home can be a huge undertaking; a CMA by Las Vegas Homes By Leslie is essential in making a smart selling decision. I provide you with a <a href="/home-evaluation.php">FREE market analysis</a> of your home and recently sold properties in your neighborhood. Together we will use this data to determine the current market value, decide on an asking price, and make the final decision to sell or hold your property.</p>
<p><a href="javascript:openPage('/contact.php');">Contact Leslie Hoke today</a> for a FREE market analysis and home consultation so you can make an educated decision and get the ball rolling toward a successful sale of your home.</p>
<h3>You Have Options</h3>
<p>If you need to sell your home but feel locked in due to depreciation, upside down in your loan, or facing foreclosure, stop guessing. YOU HAVE OPTIONS. With the many short sale programs available, there is no reason someone should be faced with foreclosure. I provide you with all of the necessary tools and resources to help you in the short sale process. Foreclosure does not have to be the answer.</p>
<h4>2. Staging Your Home</h4>
<p><img style="float: right;" title="Selling your home in Las Vegas with Leslie Hoke" src="/images/selling_your_home_in_las_vegas_with_leslie_hoke_478.jpg" alt="Selling your home in Las Vegas with Leslie Hoke" width="348" height="233" align="left" /></p>
<p>On average, a properly staged home sells for $3K-$4K more in 11 fewer days. That’s a significant impact!</p>
<p>Every person that views your home is a potential buyer. They are looking for things that are wonderful and wrong. If they find something wrong, it could affect your asking price. It’s essential to show your home in the best condition, therefore driving up the price, and ideally receiving multiple offers.</p>
<p>I will personally advise you and make suggestions to help make your home stand apart from the competition. </p>
<h4>3. Photography / Video</h4>
<p>A picture tells a thousand words. In our highly competitive Las Vegas market, the first impression is the most important part of the selling process. After staging has been completed, I take professional quality photos / video to showcase your home. This is key in persuading potential buyers to schedule showings.</p>
<h4>4. The Right Exposure</h4>
<p>In marketing your home, I develop a listing that emphasizes its unique and sellable aspects. I put your home in front of buyers, establishing it on the <a title="Las Vegas MLS" href="/idx/" target="_blank">Las Vegas MLS</a>, search engines, social media, real estate publications &amp; blogs, and my personal worldwide network of professional real estate contacts and buyers. Your home is exposed to thousands of perspective buyers across multiple platforms.</p>
<h4>5. Effective Internet Marketing - 1,000,000 + Impressions</h4>
<p><img style="float: right;" title="Selling your Las Vegas Home with Leslie Hoke" src="/images/selling_your_las_vegas_home_with_leslie_hoke_388.jpg" alt="Selling your Las Vegas Home with Leslie Hoke" width="328" height="190" align="left" />My three-tier marketing strategy includes national, regional, and social media exposure. In addition to the standard industry MLS listing, yard sign and open house marketing strategies, your home becomes a "<a title="Las Vegas Homes By Leslie Featured Listings" href="/featured-listings.php" target="_blank">Featured Listing</a>" on my highly trafficked Las Vegas real estate website and blog "Las Vegas Homes By Leslie" with its very own "Detailed Listing Page".</p>
<h4>6. National Exposure</h4>
<p>Your detailed listing page is promoted on a wide cross-section of news, financial, and real estate media websites.</p>
<p>Leading national websites Include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Google News</li>
<li>Yahoo News</li>
<li>Yahoo Finance</li>
<li>ABC, CBS and Fox</li>
<li>Trulia, Zillow and Realtor.com</li>
<li>Online news blogs</li>
<li>Real Estate Industry Trade sites</li>
<li>International News sites</li>
</ul>
<h4>7. Regional Exposure</h4>
<p>Your listing is seen on the following regional level platforms:</p>
<ul>
<li>Regional news sites,</li>
<li>Popular local news websites,</li>
<li>Websites of popular radio stations with large listener bases</li>
<li>Websites of popular television channels</li>
</ul>
<h4>8. Social Media Exposure</h4>
<p>Your property is shared on "Las Vegas Homes By Leslie" social accounts and across the most popular social media channels including:</p>
<ul>
<li>Facebook</li>
<li>Twitter</li>
<li>LinkedIn</li>
<li>YouTube</li>
<li>StumbleUpon</li>
<li>Delicious</li>
<li>Tumblr</li>
<li>Reddit and more...</li>
</ul>
<p>I ensure your listing is tweeted on 150+ news-related Twitter accounts with a combined base of 350,000+ Twitter followers and shared on Facebook pages with a combined like base of 500,000+ Facebook users. I also distribute your listing to more than 250,000 subscribers and as many as 30,000 bloggers and journalists through my personal Vocus/PRWeb.com account.  That’s exposure to over <strong><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">1.1 million</span></em></strong> potential buyers though social media alone.</p>
<img title="Selling a Home in Las Vegas - Homes By Leslie Syndication Partners" src="/images/selling_a_home_in_las_vegas_-_homes_by_leslie_syndication_partners_763.jpg" alt="Selling a Home in Las Vegas - Homes By Leslie Syndication Partners" width="673" height="519" />
<h3> </h3>
<h4>9. Search Engine Optimization and Pay-Per Click Marketing</h4>
<p>For even more targeted buyers I use SEO (search engine optimization) and PPC (pay per click) marketing.</p>
<p>Your "Detailed Listings Page" is indexed and ranked by all the leading search engines including Google, Yahoo and Bing.</p>
<h4>10. Effective Communication and Follow Up through Seller Updates</h4>
<p>I personally contact all potential buyers, or their respected agents, after each showing to collect feedback about your property. I provide a weekly report, and contact you frequently to discuss progress, updates or changes in local market conditions.</p>
<p class="important highlight"> <strong>*</strong>When you list your home with "Las Vegas Homes By Leslie" all the marketing features in my plan come at <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">NO</span></strong> additional cost to you the home seller.</p>
